item.title: CVE-2023-5601|2024-08-02T08:07:32.111Z -- unknown -- woocommerce%20ninja%20forms%20product%20add-ons
item.description: The WooCommerce Ninja Forms Product Add-ons WordPress plugin before 1.7.1 does not validate the file to be uploaded, allowing any unauthenticated users to upload arbitrary files to the server, leading to RCE.
